Name: Holt
Description: The Division of Holt consists of part of the Casey City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: Light industry, retail, education and training, manufacturing, health care and construction.
NameDerivation: Named in honour of the Rt Hon. Harold Edward Holt CH, 1908-67. Holt was Prime Minister of Australia (1966-67) and a Member of the House of Representatives (1935-67).
Members:

  • Evans, G J (ALP) 1996-1999
  • Duffy, M J (ALP) 1980-1996
  • Yates, W (LP) 1975-1980
  • Oldmeadow, M W (ALP) 1972-1975
DemographicRating: Outer Metropolitan - situated in capital cities and containing large areas of recent suburban expansion.
